Fri Oct 18 09:50:00 UTC 2017 - toms@opensuse.org

Version 0.4.6

Enhancements:
 * Transform <seealso> tag in <formalpara> (#16, #17)
 * Ignore <manpage> tag, but use its text (#18, #19)
 * Enhance own documentation (#22)
 * Add --help-xsl-param option (#24)
 * Improve code coverate & test cases (#2, #26, #27)
 * When <references> contains both @refuri and text, add text
   only to <link> when it is different from @refuri (#29)
 * Support <desc> element (#34)
 * Rename .pip -> .txt to support GitHub's vulnerability report (#39)
 * Update deprecated installing step in README.rst (#40)
 * Adjust exclusions for uniformity in setup.cfg (#45)
 * Move doc* directories to data (#49, #50)
 * Switch to DocBook 5 output format (#3, #51)
 * Correct entry/inline elements (coming from a support_matrix directive) (#55, #56)
 
Bugfixes:
 * Catch XMLSyntaxError when XML isn't well-formed (#9)
 * Ignore <meta> and <raw/> (#20, #23)
 * Fix double '.xml' suffixes (#25)
 * Ignore xml:base attributes after rst2xml conversion (#28)
 * Check for empty screen (#38)
 * Copy namespace nodes to root element (#36)
 * Update deprecated function:
   inspect.getargspec(func) -> inspect.getfullargspec(func) (#47)
 * Fixed internal refuri reference bug (#41, #52)
 * Remove empty namespace in <emphasis> (#53, 54)
 * Correct entry/inline elements (#55, #56)

