Tue Apr 18 08:51:00 UTC 2017 - toms@opensuse.org

Version 0.4.5:
 * Use good logging practise
   * Get rid of rstxml2db.log and in doc
   * Introduce "logging.conf" file
     * Add *.conf to package_data key (setup.py)
     * Include *.conf in MANIFEST.in
   * Use "log = logging.getLogger(__name__)" mantra
   * Only investigate functions from our modules in
     test_docstrings.py
   * Add pycodestyle section
   * Use log config files and fallback
 * Refactoring: move main() into cli.py


